title: Myanmar Consumer Price Index Cpi
description: Consumer Price Index CPI in Myanmar increased to 203.18 points in June from 199.31 points in May of 2022. Consumer Price Index CPI in Myanmar averaged 139.37 points from 2013 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 203.18 points in June of 2022 and a record low of 100.87 points in March of 2013. This page provides - Myanmar Consumer Price Index Cpi- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Central Statistics Organization, Myanmar
